The RIA is a state agency that is responsible for the development and maintenance of the Estonian e-identity and e-services. The RIA is also responsible for the development of the Estonian e-Residency programme. The e-Residency programme is a government-issued digital identity available to anyone in the world interested in conducting business online with Estonia.
